entry.title: Bitcoin v0.3.23 released
entry.summary: The update includes minor changes to the released files. The Linux tarball has been regenerated with a properly named directory inside, and a Win32 .zip archive has been added. Additionally, PGP-signed SHA1SUM.asc has also been added to SF. The updated checksums have been listed in the message, including the hash value of each file. Jeff Garzik, from exMULTI Inc., has signed off the message.
